    <a href="/login"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Log In</button></a><br/><br/>
    <div class="container text-center">
        <div class="row row2 hover-effect">
          <div class="col" style="color: #16bac5;">
        <br/><br/>
            Songgestions is a music based app that harnesses the power of artificial intelligence in order to cater to your 
            individual musical tastes and preferences! You'll also be able to discover new music you never knew existed as 
